<figureCitation box="[951,1058,750,777]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="29.[189,232,1928,1954]" captionTargetBox="[209,1380,270,1901]" captionTargetId="figure-59@29.[208,1380,264,1907]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="Fig. 15. ♀♀ of Muscidae Latreille, 1802. A. Myospila bimaculata (Macquart, 1834), detail of wing showing CS1–3, dorsal view. B. Mydaea ancilla (Meigen, 1826), detail of wing showing CS1–3, dorsal view. C. M. affinis Meade, 1891, detail of wing showing CS1–3, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6784161" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6784161/files/figure.png" pageId="28" pageNumber="122">Fig. 15B</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
